{"word":"μελίζω","slug":"μελίζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>μελίζω</b></el> <el>(μελίζω,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:μέλος'><el>μέλος</el></a> II\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to modulate, sing, warble</i>, <b><a href='S:Theocritus'>Theocr.</a></b>: mostly in <a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a>, <b><a href='S:Theocritus'>Theocr.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:transitive'>trans.</a> <i>to sing of, celebrate in song</i>, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}